All Nobel Laureates in Physics

The Nobel Prize in Physics has been awarded to 178 persons since 1901.

* 2005 - Roy J. Glauber, John L. Hall, Theodor W. Hänsch

* 2004 - David J. Gross, H. David Politzer, Frank Wilczek
